description: TIMBERLAND LEATHER RFID WALLET WITH REMOVABLE PASSCASE - A functional compact wallet with lots of storage, 6 credit card pockets, 2 slip pockets, 2 cash bill pocket, a removable flip pocket and RFID Protection. WHAT IS RFID? RFID stands for Radio Frequency Identification Denoting, it is the use of radio waves to identify objects carrying encoded chips. This can include credit card information, passport identification or other forms of ID and access cards. WHY SHOULD I BUY A RFID WALLET? With credit cards and debit cards moving to RFID Chips, there is a growing concern of identify theft and electronic pickpocketing. Thieves are skimming and stealing credit card information from unexpected individuals. Now is the time to protect yourself and upgrade your wallet. Keep your information safe while still looking trendy.  EACH TIMBERLAND RFID WALLET FOR MEN INCLUDES: - 100% Genuine leather exterior  - 6 standard sized credit card pockets  - 2 slip pockets  - Removable Passcase wallet (features 2 ID Windows)  - A large horizontal cash pocket split into 2 pockets  - RFID blocking protection  - Size 4.25" x 3.5"   THE PERFECT MENS MONEY ORGANIZER: With so much storage one might think this wallet would be bulky, but your wrong. We designed this mens wallet to be compact and thin so it will fit nicely in your front pocket or your back pocket. With the function of a large wallet and the benefits of a slim wallet our wallet is one of the best mens wallets available.

aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
COCHOA’s are bright colored, medium-sized, quiet and elusive birds, found in Southeast Asian forests that live on fruits, insects and molluscs. These birds love their wild and natural habitat. Similarly, we at COCHOA, love to create leather goods that have a natural look, feel and touch. 
We are as wild as our inspirational bird, who loves to challenge anything that is artificial and man-made. 
Leather is nature’s gift to mankind and is also our material of choice, since the owner of this brand comes from a family, which has been engaged in the leather trade for the past 4 generations. 
At COCHOA, we bring you years of experience in making TOP GRAIN leather goods, that will last for years to come, and will become unique with every use. 
PREMIUM QUALITY TOP GRAIN LEATHER 
COCHOA BI-FOLD wallets are made from Top Grain Real Leather. 
As a brand our founding principles are to make products that last a lifetime and age with grace. 
What better material can attain such a property than REAL LEATHER! 
PERFECT TRAVEL COMPANION 
This Real Leather wallet from COCHOA, is your perfect travel companion.
Whether you need to go down the street to your regular grocery store, or to your favorite restaurant, this wallet has you covered.
It has ample space to keep all your cards and currencies at one place.
Being a classic bi-fold, these wallets are a go-to, all-round choice for every day or even for days when you are travelling to a foreign destination, since its never too bulky to carry these wallets in your pockets.
Its constructed keeping in mind the need of the modern man, who likes to keep things simple and organised.
NO WASTED SPACE 
When we were making this wallet, we wanted to be sure that there are no wasted space.
After a lot of trials and research, we were able to make this wallet in dimensions of 4"x3.25"x0.75".
These dimensions for a Bi-fold wallet are a new standard, as most of the wallets available are quite large, which makes it uncomfortable to keep them in your back or front pockets.
However, this is not the case with this wallet. When you place this bi-fold in your pant pockets, you shall notice that it takes up very less space than the other bi-folds.
On the other hand, this wallet is still spacious as it holds as many cards and currencies as the other bi-folds. So if you are looking for a spacious yet light wallet, then you can surely settle for this one.
FEATURES AND FUNCTIONALITY 
2 ID WINDOWS 
With the help of 2 ID Windows, this wallet helps you to carry 2 Identification cards. 
Carry your Driver's License along with your Medical card in one wallet. 
	
10 CREDIT CARD SLOTS 
High on Capacity? Thats right! 
You can carry 10 Credit cards in this wallet at one go. 
	
RFID BLOCKING 
The RFID blocking feature of this wallet, will let you carry this wallet anywhere without any risk of your cards data being stolen. 
Equipped with High Grade RFID protection, this wallet Blocks signals upto 13.56 MHz. 
	
GIFT READY

Whether its Christmas, Easters, Halloweens, Father's Day, Anniversary, Birthdays, Valentines, this bi-fold wallet shall surely leave a lasting impression, and shall be cherished for a long time.

description: TIMBERLAND PRO CORDURA RFID BLOCKING TRIFOLD WALLET - A trifold wallet with lots of storage, 13 credit card pockets, 1 cash bill pocket, 1 ID window, RFID Protection, a Gift Box and a hook and loop closure. WHAT IS RFID? - RFID stands for Radio Frequency Identification Denoting, it is the use of radio waves to identify objects carrying encoded chips. This can include credit card information, passport identification or other forms of ID and access cards. WHY SHOULD I BUY A RFID WALLET? - With credit cards and debit cards moving to RFID Chips, there is a growing concern of identify theft and electronic pickpocketing. Thieves are skimming and stealing credit card information from unexpected individuals. Now is the time to protect yourself and upgrade your wallet to a new Timberland Pro RFID credit card protector. Keep your information safe while still looking trendy. Each Timberland Pro RFID Blocking Trifold Wallet Includes: - Cordura Material - 13 standard sized credit card pockets - Hook and loop closure - 1 clear ID Window - A large horizontal cash pocket - RFID blocking protection - Shipped in a tin Gift Box - Size 4.25" x 3.5" THE PERFECT MENS MONEY ORGANIZER - With so much storage one might think this wallet would be bulky, but your wrong. We designed this mens wallet to be compact and thin so it will fit nicely in your front pocket or your back pocket. With the function of a large wallet and the benefits of a slim wallet our wallet is one of the best mens wallets available.
